    <AgendaSection header="SASS through Vite">
        <section>
            <h3>SASS through Vite</h3>
            <p>Couldn't be simpler</p>
            <p>With Vite installed:</p>   
            <ol>
                <li class="fragment">install SASS<br>
                    <code>npm install --save-dev sass</code>
                </li>
                <li class="fragment">In your JS file you import the SASS files<br>
                    <code>import "./sass/style.scss";</code>
                </li>
            </ol>
        </section>
    </AgendaSection>
    <AgendaSection header="The Syntax">
        <section>
            <p><a href="https://sass-lang.com/guide">https://sass-lang.com/guide</a></p>
            
            <p>Let's go through the link above, and then</p>
            <p><a href="https://devhints.io/sass">https://devhints.io/sass</a></p>
        </section>
    </AgendaSection>
    <AgendaSection header="Exercice">
        <section>
            <p>Play around with SASS</p>
            <ol>
                <li>Install SASS in a / your project</li>
                <li>Create a SASS file</li>
                <li>Import it in JS</li>
            </ol>
        </section>
    </AgendaSection>

    <AgendaSection header="A cool trick">
        <section>
            <Code code={snippets["cool-trick.scss"]} language="sass" />
            <p class="fragment">becomes</p>
            <div class="fragment"><Code code={snippets["cool-trick.css"]} language="css" /></div>
        </section>
